2008-11-24  Zeeshan Ali (Khattak)  <zeeshanak@gnome.org>

	* src/av-cp/playlist-treeview.c:
	* src/universal-cp/action-dialog.c:

        Add missing casts. Patch by Sven Neumann <s.neumann@phase-zero.de>.

